Internet Explorer 9 and 10

On the web browser "gear" Tools menu select "Internet options". (Please note that the gear menu can also be shown by pressing the Alt-X key combination)
In the "Internet Options" window select the "Security" tab.
Directly above the OK, Cancel, and Apply buttons, click the "Reset all zones to default level" button.
In the "Internet Options" window click on the "OK" button to close it.
Click on the "Refresh" button of the web browser to refresh the page, or press the F5 key

